            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>科斯塔集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CSGP:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CSGP\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CSGP-US</a>)截至台北時間30日02:59股價下跌3.28美元，報61.92美元，跌幅5.03%，成交量2,234,764（股），盤中最高價65.46美元、最低價61.92美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.24%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.64%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-1.4%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-0.76%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>科斯塔集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CSGP:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CSGP\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CSGP-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+2.24%</li> <li>近 1 月：-1.18%</li> <li>近 3 月：-15.35%</li> <li>近 6 月：-29.07%</li> <li>今年以來：-1.52%</li></ul></section></main>",
